 How it works 1. Download the Eggciting Easter App from your phone app store.  2. You can also scan the QR code that you will find in Riverside Mall.  3. Use the Eggciting Easter App to find the six virtual bunnies throughout Riverside mall. 4. They are located at the info kiosk, Wimpy, the Food court, Nevills, King Pie and Gen X – elephant court. You are welcome to use the free wi-fi that is available at Riverside Mall. 4. Once you have six bunnies you can collect your chocolate egg at the info kiosk, take  a virtual selfie with the Easter bunny and then you’ll be automatically entered into the draw for great prizes!  *T’s and C’s apply.